import React, { useState } from 'react'; function Search() { const [searchQuery, setSearchQuery] = useState(''); const [filters, setFilters] = useState({ dateRange: 'all', organization: '', lobbyist: '', category: 'all' }); const handleSearch = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); // Search functionality will be implemented here console.log('Search query:', searchQuery, 'Filters:', filters); }; return (

Advanced Search

Search through CA lobby data with powerful filtering and analysis tools

setSearchQuery(e.target.value)} placeholder="Search for lobbyists, organizations, bills, or topics..." className="search-input" />

Advanced Filters

setFilters({...filters, organization: e.target.value})} placeholder="Filter by organization name" disabled />
setFilters({...filters, lobbyist: e.target.value})} placeholder="Filter by lobbyist name" disabled />

Search Features

Advanced search capabilities will include:

  • Full-text search across all lobby documents
  • Boolean operators (AND, OR, NOT)
  • Wildcard and fuzzy matching
  • Phrase and proximity searches
  • Auto-complete and search suggestions

Filter Options

Comprehensive filtering by:

  • Date ranges and time periods
  • Organization and entity types
  • Spending amounts and thresholds
  • Geographic regions and districts
  • Document types and categories

Search Results

Results will be displayed with:

Sample Result 1

Lobbyist registration for XYZ Corporation - Healthcare sector

Filed: Sept 15, 2024 | Amount: $50,000

Sample Result 2

Quarterly activity report - Technology lobbying

Filed: Sept 10, 2024 | Amount: $25,000

Export & Save

Search result options:

  • Export results to CSV, Excel, or PDF
  • Save search queries for future use
  • Set up alerts for new matching results
  • Share search results with team members
); } export default Search;
